Dear Customer,

 * Due to important notice, this e-mail is sent to members including those who have not subscribed to our e-mail newsletter.
 * This e-mail is sent to ANA Mileage Club Members.

----------------------------------

[ Important Notice from ANA ]
Termination of the Upgrade Points service

----------------------------------

Thank you very much for supporting the ANA Group.

Please be informed that the Upgrade Points service offered to ANA Premium Members and Super Flyers primary members will end as of FY2026.

Please note that the following services currently available using Upgrade Points will continue to be available through using miles.
- Seating class upgrades
- Lounge access

Lounge services that are currently available only with Upgrade Points will be able to be used with miles in the future.
We will announce the start date of the service on the ANA Website as soon as it is determined.

- For more details, click here
 http://amc.ana.co.jp/?4_--_329845_--_1258403_--_10 

The following services will be terminated as of March 31, 2027 (JST), following the termination of this Upgrade Points offer.
Seat upgrade service with Upgrade Points exclusively for ANA Diamond Service members
 http://amc.ana.co.jp/?4_--_329845_--_1258403_--_11 

As a token of our appreciation for your patronage, we are offering 50,000 miles to Diamond Service members who become Diamond Service members in fiscal year 2027.
The mileage will be credited to Diamond Service members as of April 1, 2027 (JST) in the mileage account group Group 4: Miles related to aviation services (Time limited) on or about April 2027.
 http://amc.ana.co.jp/?4_--_329845_--_1258403_--_12 

We will continue to make further improvements to our mileage program and services to ensure customer satisfaction.

We look forward to you will continue to use our services going forward.


 Check out the detailed contents of this e-mail by visiting
 http://amc.ana.co.jp/?4_--_329845_--_1258403_--_13 


